<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":{"file":"3779152-fulllogo-7-1024x819.jpg","path":"10\/103881\/","mime":"image\/jpeg","sizes":"scale_super,scale_small,square_medium,square_small,scale_medium,square_tiny,square_mini,square_avatar,screen_medium,screen_kubrick,scale_large,scale_avatar","caption":null},"background":[]}' />
==Overview== Margarite Entertainment is a video game publisher that focuses on licensing older games to re-release on more modern platforms. The first game published by Margarite was [[Games/Big_Rigs_Over_the_Road_Racing|Big Rigs: Over the Road Racing]] on April 8th 2025. At the time of Big Rigs release, no other games were announced. On July 7th, 2025, Margarite announced their second published game, [[Games/Gold_Miner|Gold Miner: Classic Edition]]. The game is a re-release on Steam of a classic Shockwave Flash game from developer [[Companies/GameRival|GameRival]].

